reviewText: OH boy this movie is so cool, Carlos Gallardo is awsome with the acting if you like EL MARIACHI OR DESPERADO YOU WOULD LIKE BRAVO it has lots of action lot of blood gore for a action movie,thats my kind of movie. i gave this movie 4 stars because the movie could use more american actors,only saw Carlos the rest of the actors are from MEXICO but is a good movie is a must have .....
